      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "So after using the platform for a bit there a few features that are not already included that I would have seen some use for. \nI realize the platform is still under construction, so just ignore me if these are already be planed. \n\nProblem: \nI initially miss configured one of my projects slot's size and wasn't subsequently able to modify it.  \nFeatures missing: \n- ability to delete a project \n- ability to modify the slot configuration of a project",
      "author": {
        "id": "509798510170865675",
        "name": "essen__",
        "discriminator": "0000",
        "nickname": "Essen",
        "color": null,
        "isBot": false,
        "roles": [],
        "avatarUrl": "2026-07_media/80e086280c9caadd9c05998c3254c9a9-25B3D.png"
      },
